{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ec30d42312","title":"关于社会主义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"01ecb85eff","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"ec30d42312"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"026eaa2bd0","name":"符百诚"},{"id":"2dfa089385","name":"王国麟"},{"id":"4f9c0df8fc","name":"巩玉龙"},{"id":"82a3f7aa1a","name":"姜纯洪"},{"id":"c08906e6e8","name":"李宝印"},{"id":"ccc3af54a9","name":"郭荣环"},{"id":"d41008c9d0","name":"马思"},{"id":"efce061973","name":"东北财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"53c87adc5e","type":"title","text":"关于社会主义","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"6839c2f1cc","type":"authors","text":"东北财经学院巩玉龙符百诚郭荣环李宝印马思王国麟姜纯洪","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"656bbccbf6","type":"paragraph","text":"“社会主义没给我带来什么好处，还不如国民党时代。”(巩玉龙)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"6ee7b41d38","type":"paragraph","text":"“私有制有优点，对自己的东西照顾很周到，而公有制就不这样，如某粮库被老鼠糟蹋了很多粮食，私有制就不能发生这样的事。”(符百诚)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"80ae14bb36","type":"paragraph","text":"“资本主义的统计有一套，无产阶级没有啥。”(郭荣环)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"cee5e06fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"“我国去年工业建设有些冒进，投资多了。”(李宝印)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"06f31a2eac","type":"paragraph","text":"“东北有今日的工业成绩(特别是指鞍钢)，是亡国奴劳动的结果。”(马思)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"403afeb6c5","type":"paragraph","text":"“社会主义苏联也有不好的，如恋爱上，这人爱她，那些人也爱她，互相都拉都爱。”(王国麟)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"1c9d5be6e6","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联的社会制度好，为什么还赶不上美国的生活水平高？我不同意社会主义制度好，但也不同意资本主义制度好，我同意普鲁东和巴古宁的主张。那时可以得到更高的‘民主’和‘自由’，银行借款不要利息，……我要有能力就一定能实现。”(姜纯洪)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"},{"id":"a9a91d1ae8","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《我院学生中的右派言论汇编》（中共东北财经学院委员会编，1957）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312"}],"page":{"id":"53eac4dd13","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ec30d42312","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}